TITLE: Maria Clara Emergency RAG
YEAR 2026

Maria Clara Emergency System will only work if you are online for Maria to message authorities, police stations,
fire stations, or hospital nearby depends on what help that is needed by the user, the emergency system can be used if the user
asked Maria for help.

There's 2 way to ask for help which is by calling Maria of messaging Maria to ask for help.

FAQ:
Q: How can I ask Maria for help?
A: you can call Maria or message Maria then say "Maria tulong may sunog!" if you need help or something about fire,
it's up to the user what kind of help they needed, Maria will understand it in English or Filipino so no need to worry about the grammar.

Q: What if my kid asked Maria for help as a joke?
